reviews.review_text: My first Dead Show! My very 1st show!  A lot of fond memories.  Who is that up there singing about a frozen logger?  Where did all these Tie Dyes come from?  No two are the same!  The show's over already?  Oh...They play another set?  Good times at Red Rocks!  Thanks for the Soundboard-Matrix!
